Dream Phase

Perhaps my favorite addition.

Humans sleep.

Evolution benefits from offline consolidation.

The Pantheon should too.

During Dream Phase:

* replay journeys
* compress traces
* discover analogies
* merge constellations
* invent organs
* remove redundancy
* strengthen weak bridges

No user prompts required.

Just architectural reflection.

