Semantic Weather

Right now your navigation assumes static oceans.

Real oceans have weather.

Weather includes:

* hype fronts
* paradigm winds
* uncertainty fog
* attention storms
* innovation lightning
* convergence currents
* stagnation doldrums

Navigation should account for the climate of ideas, not just their geometry.

